  10 |            | \begin{example}
  11 |            | 
  12 |            | Application: predicting global population.
  13 |            | 
  14 |            | Population is a function $u(t)$ of time $t$.
  15 |            | 
  16 |            | Express this as:
  17 |            |  \begin{description}
